---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import meLargeImage from '../images/me-large.jpg'
import type { getEntries, getEntry } from 'astro:content'
---

<Layout title="About Me">
	<main class="relative grow p-12">
		<div class="absolute left-0 top-0 z-0 h-full w-5/12 bg-slate-600"></div>
		<div class="relative z-10 m-auto grid w-9/12 grid-cols-2">
			<div class="flex flex-col items-center bg-slate-300 p-12 drop-shadow-2xl">
				<Image
					class="inline-block h-96 w-96 rounded-full object-cover ring-2 ring-white"
					src={meLargeImage}
					alt="me"
				/>
				<br />
				<h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold">Eric Lavigne</h1>
				<hr class="my-6 w-7/12 border-b border-slate-700" />
				<h2 class="text-xl uppercase">Staff Engineer - Team Lead</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="prose prose-slate flex flex-col items-start p-12">
				<div class="flex">
					<div class="typing-animation">
						<h1 class="my-0 overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap font-mono text-6xl">
							Hello world!
						</h1>
					</div>
				</div>
				<h2>A Bit About Me</h2>
				<p class="">
					Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis a tortor risus. Sed mollis
					urna ac erat vulputate, vitae sagittis lacus ornare. Nam nec gravida felis. Phasellus
					fringilla quam ex, non tincidunt augue gravida vitae. Ut nec lectus ex. Integer id lorem
					in magna egestas dictum at vitae orci. Etiam eu maximus arcu. Nam id scelerisque metus, eu
					mollis nibh. Praesent egestas ex vel lobortis dignissim. Sed pellentesque id ligula id
					posuere. Nulla tincidunt et felis in interdum. Maecenas nibh erat, aliquam nec aliquet
					non, ultrices et mi. Integer elit felis, bibendum et porta mollis, eleifend feugiat
					tortor.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* The typing effect */
	@keyframes typing {
		from {
			width: 0;
		}
		to {
			width: 100%;
		}
	}

	/* The typewriter cursor effect */
	@keyframes blink-caret {
		from,
		to {
			border-color: transparent;
		}
		50% {
			border-color: #a8a29e;
		}
	}

	.typing-animation {
		display: block;
		border-right-width: 0.15em;
		animation:
			typing 2.5s steps(12, end),
			blink-caret 0.75s step-end infinite;
	}
</style>
